    Function reference

    All functions

    cluster.coefs()
    Fuzzy c-medoids clustering on tensor-product spline coefficients
    cluster.fitted()
    Fuzzy c-medoids clustering on fitted values of splines
    FKM.glm()
    Fit a generalized linear model (GLM) using clusters a predictors
    plot(<FKM.glm>)
    Plot glm that uses clusters as predictors
    plot(<FKM.predicted>)
    Plot an object of class FKM.predicted
    plot(<FKM.TPS>)
    Plot an object of class 'FKM.TPS'
    plot(<TPSfit>)
    Plot an object of class TPSfit.
    predict(<FKM.glm>)
    Predict the model outcome for a new set of data
    predict(<FKM.TPS>)
    Predict the cluster assignment for new subjects
    TPSfit()
    Fit tensor product splines to longitudinal data
    TS.sim.new
    A data frame of simulated multivariate time series data for predictions
    TS.sim
    A data frame of simulated multivariate time series data
